          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We have bade the world goodbye."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "We've been called to be His pure and spotless Bride;"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Where we'll soon behold our Jesus"
            }
